            },
            {
                "comment": "Very nice guy. Go to the lectures cause the topics he talks about are what is tested. idk why most people skipped lectures, & i think they would have done better grade-wise if they went. take good notes in class.",
                "difficulty_rating": 3,
                "quality_rating": 5
            },
            {
                "comment": "He really knows how to teach well and gives you all the material you need to do well on tests. He is also really interesting and often likes to talk about new research on the frontier of microbiology. He is also very responsive to questions and very helpful in his office outside of class. I just wish I'd get teachers like him more often.",
                "difficulty_rating": 3,
                "quality_rating": 5
            },
            {
                "comment": "This guys knows how to teach. He provides clear explanations for all processes and pathways and provides all materials needed to do well. Questions the day before the exam and even allows extra credit points on Fridays for sending in confusing topics. Highly suggest taking his class if you like metabolism!",
